Step 1: Add the MDT Boot Image to WDS

    1. Open Windows Deployment Services from Server Manager.
    2. Expand Servers → Right-click your WDS Server → Select Add Boot Image.
    3. Browse to the MDT boot image:

    	D:\DeploymentShare\Boot\LiteTouchPE_x64.wim

    4. Click Next, then Finish.

Step 2: Configure PXE Boot Policy

    1. Open WDS management console.
    2. Right-click Server → Click Properties → Navigate to PXE Response.
    3. Choose:

        Respond to all clients (known and unknown)

        Check Require administrator approval if necessary.
